00:24:35,765 --> 00:24:36,345
movies are.

309
00:24:36,345 --> 00:24:45,273
It's also extremely cool to involve your talented animators in the pre-production phase, because

310
00:24:45,273 --> 00:24:50,537
of course they have so many great ideas about moment-to-moment action, and you can all start

