00:34:54,117 --> 00:34:56,399
and we had to make a memory sacrifice in order

460
00:34:56,399 --> 00:34:59,741
to achieve the triple buffering solution that finally

461
00:34:59,741 --> 00:35:01,122
got rid of the tearing.

462
00:35:01,122 --> 00:35:05,405
Now, this is an issue that plagues many teams, I know.

463
00:35:05,405 --> 00:35:08,147
And we just wanted to stand up and say that the only way

464
00:35:08,147 --> 00:35:11,289
that we were able to tackle it was to regard it

465
00:35:11,289 --> 00:35:12,890
as a very serious problem.

