00:54:37,185 --> 00:54:43,251
of the Year awards. So I quickly wanted to thank and congratulate everyone at Naughty

732
00:54:43,251 --> 00:54:48,876
Dog and at Sony and all of our partners beyond the studio who have helped our game become

733
00:54:48,876 --> 00:54:49,517
such a big hit.

