743
00:55:31,518 --> 00:55:33,619
In short, we work in a very fast, loose, seat-of-the-pants way.

744
00:55:40,961 --> 00:55:47,046
that puts an emphasis on our team members taking responsibility for the production and

745
00:55:47,046 --> 00:55:52,711
organization of their own work and for the design of the game.

