00:55:52,711 --> 00:55:58,076
We encourage our team to stay constructively critical and honest with each other at all

747
00:55:58,076 --> 00:56:04,281
times and to always keep an open mind about our design and production process to make

748
00:56:04,281 --> 00:56:08,145
sure that we're working in the best ways that we can possibly work.

749
00:56:09,412 --> 00:56:12,674
We always take the time to listen to each other respectfully

750
