and we never make things personal.

751
00:56:15,236 --> 00:56:19,318
We always have to remember that we're all in it working together

752
00:56:19,318 --> 00:56:21,840
towards the greatness of the game.

753
00:56:21,840 --> 00:56:27,663
And working in a way that builds strong collaborative relationships between our

754
00:56:27,663 --> 00:56:28,363
team members

